@devoncarew turns out there's an easy fix for this (thanks @sigurdm / @jonasfj!) by using `dart run test:test` instead of `dart [pub-snapshot] run test`.

The Dart-Code change is here (I've also reverted the previous workaround) and is gated on v2.12 of the SDK:

https://github.com/Dart-Code/Dart-Code/pull/2956/commits/c7f81d6324a819946609ffca0ef1956a21c5a771
